        //---------------------------------------------------------------------
        // SECTION [ WORKS ]
        div.section.section--work
            div.l-center
                // Header
                +Header({activePage: 'Work'})

                // Standard section's blocks
                div.section__title Our work
                div.section__description.section__description--work Cras suscipit porttitor porttitor. Morbi sit amet tincidunt sapien. Curabitur posuere lectus aliquet erat rutrum sollicitudin. In enim diam, ullamcorper quis libero et, ultricies commodo est. Quisque at ante vitae justo fermentum viverra ac eu justo. Ut luctus imperdiet lacus, eget laoreet erat posuere quis.

